nb handle catch exception junit test
Harrah, M.  20060501.  Exception handling in JUnit tests.
Platinum solutions: Matt Harrah's blog.
http://blog.platinumsolutions.com/node/113

In my mind there is one, and only one, good reason to catch Exceptions
thrown by code under test in a JUnit test: when you are actually testing
that the code under tests throws Exceptions according to its contract.


